reviewText: The line-up is always all of that with Steve Harvey and so many more comics that made my evening. I love to laugh.
Title: Def Comedy Jam All-Stars Vol. 4

reviewText: This is HOT! Check out the early years of some of the greatest comedians of our time; Dave Chapell, Bernie Mac, DL Hughley, Steve Harvey, amongst others!
Title: Def Comedy Jam All-Stars Vol. 4

reviewText: A welcome addition to my comedy library, these maturing comics are perfecting their styles, and on stage deliveries. Dave Chappell is at the beginning of his profitable career, with many more years hopefully to follow. Young talented comics are becoming harder to find.
Title: Def Comedy Jam All-Stars Vol. 4

reviewText: This is worth your money, makes you bust a gut, Steve Harvey, Bernie Mac is greatest of all, D. L. Hughley is funny
Title: Def Comedy Jam All-Stars Vol. 4

reviewText: These are classic videos and good to have in your collection. They are priceless. I'm trying to get the one with Bernie Mac coming out: "I ain't scared of you MFs" I laughed until i cried and screamed the whole time during his set. I got to know what volume it is on so I can buy it.
Title: Def Comedy Jam All-Stars Vol. 4

reviewText: This one was funny as well as the first 3 volumes. Great price and I reccommend it to any one.
Title: Def Comedy Jam All-Stars Vol. 4
